            "heading": "Measuring Guide",
            "icon": "heart",
            "content": "<h3>Head & Neck</h3><ul><li><strong>Head Circumference:</strong> Measure the circumference of the head at forehead level.</li><li><strong>Neck:</strong> Measure around the base of the neck where a shirt collar sits.</li></ul><h3>Upper Body</h3><ul><li><strong>Shoulders:</strong> Measure on the back from where the sleeves would attach.</li><li><strong>Chest:</strong> Measure the full circumference of the chest at nipple level.</li><li><strong>Stomach:</strong> Measure the circumference of the midsection at belly button level.</li><li><strong>Torso:</strong> Measure vertically from the base of the neck to the waistline.</li></ul><h3>Arms & Hands</h3><ul><li><strong>Sleeve Length:</strong> Measure from the shoulder point down to the wrist bone.</li><li><strong>Bicep:</strong> Measure the circumference of the arm at its widest point.</li><li><strong>Wrist:</strong> Measure the circumference of the arm at the wrist bone.</li><li><strong>Palm Circumference:</strong> Measure around the widest part of the hand, excluding the thumb.</li><li><strong>Hand Length:</strong> Measure from the wrist crease to the tip of the middle finger.</li></ul><h3>Suspenders</h3><ul><li><strong>Strap Length:</strong> Measure from the center-back waistband, over the shoulder, to the front belt line.</li><li><strong>Back Rise:</strong> Measure vertically from the center-back waistband to the base of the neck.</li></ul><h3>Waist & Pelvis</h3><ul><li><strong>Waist:</strong> Measure around the body at the level where the belt is worn.</li><li><strong>Hips:</strong> Measure the circumference of the widest part of the seat.</li><li><strong>Crotch:</strong> Measure from the top of the front waistband, over the genitals, to the taint.</li><li><strong>Butt Rise:</strong> Measure from the center-back waistband down to the start of the crotch seam.</li></ul><h3>Legs</h3><ul><li><strong>Inseam:</strong> Measure the inside of the leg from the crotch to the ankle bone.</li><li><strong>Upper Thigh:</strong> Measure the circumference of the leg at the widest part of the thigh.</li><li><strong>Lower Thigh:</strong> Measure the circumference of the leg just above the knee.</li><li><strong>Knee:</strong> Measure the circumference of the leg at the center of the knee.</li><li><strong>Calf:</strong> Measure the circumference of the lower leg at its widest point.</li><li><strong>Ankle:</strong> Measure the circumference of the leg at the ankle bone.</li><li><strong>Length:</strong> For kilts, measure from the waist to the center of the knee.</li></ul>",
